{
  "stem": "24242.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the height of the winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came to us in the height of the winter of 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You asked me who took care of the people during the summer of '42.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had my three brothers, Tuvia, Asael, and Zisl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Again, it's hard for me-- I'll do it to the best of my ability.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's going to be hard for you to believe-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hard to comprehend, even, never mind believing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you were in the company of-- of those three brothers-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you felt like you have a whole army behind you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were fearless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were not afraid of anybody if they were in your-- if you were in their company, you are fearless.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- Tuvia and Zisl were over 6 feet tall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very powerful men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Asael was somewhat shorter, 5' 8' or 5' 9', but I think strength-wise was probably-- Tuvia and Asael strengthwise, they were very healthy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were down-to-earth people-- farmers, which this is-- I mean, I'm giving you my personal opinion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if you'll agree or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There is a different-- when a person grows up in the city in luxury or a person grows up on a farm, and from his childhood, he had to take care of himself because he was-- because his religion is Jewish-- this is my own interpretation.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [BACKGROUND NOISE] I'll tell you-- give you an example what my brothers were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll give you an example on one-- Zisl Alexander.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] There was a man in Israel that he was bending steel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
